The Permanent Secretary in the Kano State Ministry of Education, Hajiya Lauratu Ado-Diso, has said there is no student casualty in a fire incident at the Government Girls College (GGC), Kano. Hajiya Lauratu revealed this through the ministry’s Deputy Director, Information, Mr Aliyu Yusuf, in a statement on Wednesday. She, therefore, called on parents to remain calm and disregard all forms of romours that might circulate about the inferno as “no single student was a casualty.” (NAN) 